data.description: Wonderful brick 3BD, 2BA Rincon Home, lots of amazing features including, 2 sets of solar panels providing incredible energy savings, upgraded double pane windows, 50 yr roof shingles w/ upgraded skylights, Florida room, LR with vaulted ceiling, all appliances remain including washer and dryer, electrical service to utility building, carport and camper/boat shed, new gas water heater and gas logs, HVAC 2 yrs old with UV light, laminate & tile floors throughout, roman blinds, fruit bearing trees, fenced backyard and more.
